Các trách nhiệm khác theo quy định Vietbank trong từng thời kỳ hoặc theo phân công của cấp có thẩm quyền.

We are seeking an enthusiastic Senior Planner/ Senior Urban Designer to join our growing Vietnam Cities, Planning and Design Team. With an exciting and innovative pipeline of work, you will help lead the delivery of projects as well as help to develop the team’s capability and depth.

As part of a regional team of urban planners, economists, transport planners and designers, you will play a key role in the winning and delivery of a wide range of exciting and city shaping projects:

• Strategic planning, economic positioning, integrated land use-mobility-engineering studies;
• Masterplanning & Urban Design Studies & Plans.
• Various multi-disciplinary studies funded by International Financial Institutions (World Bank, ADB etc.);
• Sustainability & urban resilience strategies;
• Supporting major infrastructure delivery team through strategic planning, technical advice, and planning approvals.
• Working with the advisory team to integrate economics, planning & design for various studies.
• Reporting to the Vietnam office leader as well as to the SE Asia Cities, Planning & Design leader.

As a senior member of the planning team, you will be required to:
• Assemble project teams to bid on and deliver projects;
• Manage the delivery of key projects across the region;
• Help to drive the shape and direction planning and design business;
• Leverage industry connections to drive work winning across Arup
• Teaching, mentoring, and managing staff
• Develop connections across Arup and contribute to planning skills networks

Quản lý điều hành chung nguồn lực và các hoạt động của Ban Dự án, đảm bảo sử dụng tối ưu các nguồn lực phục vụ công tác bán hàng, phát triển bán hàng và quản lý dự án hiệu quả.
1. Quản lý và phát triển tổ chức của Ban Dự án
2. Quản lý, kiểm soát việc thực hiện mục tiêu của Ban Dự án
